{"tid":2476350,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同佢食完一餐飯，搞到自己有d迷惘","createTime":"2021-04-05T12:13:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-06T20:48:18.000Z","uid":164888,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cc2984eb052372bf6d40ce5790e34671e3ad1778","tid":2476350,"uid":164888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T12:13:15.000Z","msg":"是咁的，細佬前排同個女同事食完餐飯<br />\n係佢主動約既<br />\n咁就搵咗間西餐廳啦<br />\n就食完個陣佢突然拎個蛋糕出黎同我慶祝生日<br />\n哇屌，一打開個蛋糕，奇奇怪怪咁<br />\n一問，原來係handmade 既<br />\n當時就好尷全場都望住哂<br />\n咁我見個場面咁尷尬就諗住詼諧下<br />\n學阿岩布仙尼咁<br />\n唱咗首happy birthday to me<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到佢係到 一直笑，笑到肚痛<br />\nOverall黎講成餐飯都食得好開心既<br />\n<br />\n送完佢去搭車之後就收到佢個msg<br />\n叫我小心d返屋企<br />\n<br />\n咁我當時其實個心真係小鹿亂撞<br />\n畢竟好耐都冇拍拖，人又步入中年<br />\n咁平時都係flirt下女又曖昧下<br />\n <br />\n同埋我同佢其實又唔係話真係好熟<br />\n又約我食飯又整蛋糕<br />\n話係普通同事朋友又好似over咗<br />\n<br />\n咁其實佢係咪對我有意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87eed083b26d61c876a6b9552982b1178174aa20","tid":2476350,"uid":277589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T12:14:34.000Z","msg":"熟到食得"},{"pid":"fd26392588b9133f2e6399a10200bef3ee721f1d","tid":2476350,"uid":158998,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T12:17:20.000Z","msg":"你講弱智嘢佢都笑到肚痛 你話呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad31d5c94e4e3a5be897ccd9a0df412f17d6f432","tid":2476350,"uid":393145,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T12:18:39.000Z","msg":"學整蛋糕俾男神啫<br />\n咁啱呢排你生日可以試蛋糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2e72dcd546c11fe6e24a0606a7f0678e554795b","tid":2476350,"uid":393145,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ad31d5c94e4e3a5be897ccd9a0df412f17d6f432","tid":2476350,"uid":393145,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T12:18:3